Plot:

Camp Beaver lake is about to be shut down by the local authorites, and Max, the owner, (Ron Jeremy) has no choice but to sell the place. Walter, (Randy Spears) a nerdy executive for a Japanese company, is sent to good real estate investment. His frustrated wife, (Danielle Rogers) convinces him to take her along for the ride. Little do they know, that it is really a nudist camp where anything goes
